# Release changelog and version sync

When working in this repo, treat any request to do a version release (for example: "release", "cut a release", "bump version", "ship version X") as requiring both of the following updates in the same change:

1. Update the root `README.md` changelog:
   - Add or update entries under `### Unreleased` for pending changes.
   - For an actual release, move relevant unreleased entries into a new version section.
2. Update the root `library.json`:
   - Set `version` to the released version.

Do not perform a release-version change that updates only one of these files.
